# .gitignore -- OAR private and generated files
# description: Keeps generated responses, local responders, caches, secrets, browser profiles, and build outputs out of source control.
# Tags: gitignore, privacy, generated-files, secrets
# date: 2026-07-04
responses/*
!responses/
agents/*
!agents/
!agents/__init__.py
!agents/COMBINER.py
!agents/chatgpt_web.py
!agents/glm_web.py
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.venv/
venv/
.env
.env.*
feedback/
config.local.*
secrets/
*.log
*.jsonl
*.sqlite
*.db
.coverage
htmlcov/
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
implementation.md
QA.md
rules.md
browser-profile*/
playwright-profile*/
*.har
*.trace.zip
screenshots/
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
